### 单个查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/noteNodes/1


### 创建对象
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/noteNodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "日语学习",
  "noteType": null,
  "sort": 10,
  "meta": {
    "icon": "测试图标",
    "tags": [
      {
        "bizType": "NOTE",
        "label": "成功",
        "className": "tag-success"
      }
    ]
  }
}
